Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是想要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.66,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38\c&HF4F4F9&\3c&H050506&\pos(687,339)}路\N亞\N釣\N法\N之\N{\c&H41A8DD&}神\N技
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然一看這種雜誌就會讓人有購買欲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～ 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要買釣竿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且一直向海咲借也怪不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 海咲人那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點我倒覺得沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 你現在是想要一個自己的釣竿是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要不要也買個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這麼過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正迷上釣魚是從擁有自己的釣具開始的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 應該要很多錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要看是什麼東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要買的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是買個好點的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我沒錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.25,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&H409350&\3c&H050506&\org(568,621)\frz18.056\pos(348,488)\fs38}期待你的{\c&H41A8DD&}HAPPY{\c&HDE5BF7&}笑臉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:38.51,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38\c&H409350&\3c&H050506&\org(568,621)\pos(1019,218)}期待你的{\c&H41A8DD&}HAPPY{\c&HDE5BF7&}笑臉哦
