Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:50.69,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\c&H20ECFF&\3c&H050506&\frz355.876\pos(594,194)}CHILIPOT漢堡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:50.69,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}{\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H8B5D41&}CHILI POT是辣椒鍋，也有髮型中的鍋蓋頭的意思。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先去看看再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 今天船長不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 是還沒有來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那先看看魚竿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚竿的話 我推薦這一邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:12.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒有噴漆鍍膜 非常輕便哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這叫做「unsanding」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.79,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H5A3F2E&\fs35}unsanding，sanding是磨毛的意思，這裡就是不磨毛。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LUNAMIS S900ML
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於初學者來說 是個不錯的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「LUNAMIS」啊 可以說是為釣海鱸而量身定做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,價格適中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個釣竿的厲害之處在於
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上擁有頂級的S系列所有的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}試著揮揮看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個很不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 握著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣子把魚竿的頂端向下壓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能看出硬度和彎曲度的差別了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的貨色才37500日元 我覺得真是撿大便宜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 要配那根釣竿的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推薦這一個線輪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,TWIN POWER C3000HG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.35,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H5A3F2E&\fs35\an8}西瑪諾紡車輪 大概要2K+
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我選的話還是「stela」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一款呢 性能很好 價錢卻相當實惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果把「stela」比作是釣魚愛好者所憧憬的公主的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一款就相當於是校園的麥當娜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 高中生的你們也能負擔得起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪看上去很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十…十萬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣竿和線輪 還有擬餌和釣線之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雜七雜八都加起來的話 差不多這個價
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想要釣魚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼些錢還是得花的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪來這麼多錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱死了熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼熱的天 人都快要化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春 你的星球也會熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會哦 超級涼快的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他認識小春？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是羡慕嫉妒恨啊 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽到了嗎 海咲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯啊 一定很適合炎炎夏日去度假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 那邊的印度人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在店裡面你就不能把頭上的包布摘掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是看看就熱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 少年 你也釣魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海咲 老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 滾燙的紅茶 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是船長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是我的大哥一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 小步是個超好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當店員不行的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣魚總可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？釣魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹 釣魚也沒法掙錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有能掙錢的路子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能讓我們三人來幫忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三個想在你的釣魚船上打工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在釣魚船上打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在盯著我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面試？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得面帶笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙對釣魚不是半吊子的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何也想要有自己的漁具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 合格！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶 合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 船長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天開始就過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多關照~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要上了我的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天就讓你成為海上男兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海上男兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是小步 真是可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 失陪下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}戀愛女神降臨了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太棒了 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}女神 我愛你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過勞動來賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過光憑這些就能提高釣魚技術了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是在船上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都可以釣個盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪要是真就這樣提高釣術的話也沒什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小島 蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  可哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好有點渴 這次就饒了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能太過去那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙在的話就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:09.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是指的誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來目的不只是釣魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H313168&\fs70\pos(292,191)}極
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H313168&\fs70\pos(995,205)}密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:18.81,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(647,700)\c&H4A7890&}duck本部長最重要案件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(486,145)\fs35}duck最重要案件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(766,231)\fs35}百慕大綜合征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(415,328)\fs35}主要現象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(647,446)\fs35}船舶消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(648,523)\fs35}船艙消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:21.48,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H050506&\pos(885,590)\fs35}船員短期失憶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百慕大綜合征就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛羅里達半島前端的波多黎各島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和百慕大列島組成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}被稱之為百慕大三角的三角形海域內發生的異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}船隻和飛機消失的無影無蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}另外指南針和機器也會出現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:32.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了 我也必須一起去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,不 這只是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這晴朗的夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是鯕鰍之日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.13,sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30\c&HF1F1F9&\3c&H5A3F2E&}鯕鰍：（學名：Coryphaenahippurus），俗名三保公魚、白虎、海(魚廉)、鬼頭刀、\N舢板跳魚鯕鰍體延長側扁，前部高大，向後漸變細。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想釣鯕鰍～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯕鰍個頭很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有差不多2米左右的傢伙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣其實不難釣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們太不老實
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拽線的力量很大 很有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表也很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興奮的時候會變顏色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想釣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙要幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要幹嘛？ 釣魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多關照了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢 果然是來對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船是會晃成這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 小春 拿抄網
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼夏樹不動如山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抄網
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抄網×N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也得去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抄網×N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分滿分！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全有問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹好狡猾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在釣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在做引導
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引導？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯕鰍引導員（instructor）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務就是釣上第一條魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種魚只要有一條上鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的魚就會跟著來咬鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人就都能釣到魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹 你這眼鏡好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是偏光鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上這個就能看清水裡的魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 好棒哦 借我戴×4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下借你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人一釣上魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就馬上去抄魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大魚的話 要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,垂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水準的話很容易折斷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪也是 拜託咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
